{
  "texts": [
    "Posterior the predictions, only the results (compound mixture in SMILES format, predicted stability score, and label) for mixtures containing ibuprofen were post-processed and then exported in the CSV format.",
    "The distribution of stability scores for mixtures containing ibuprofen as predicted by both classifiers are shown in Fig. 6.",
    "Using this strategy, approximately 2% out of the NADES/DES Universe presented ibuprofen in its composition.",
    "Within these, 9% of those mixtures were predicted to be stable by classifier Alpha; while this percentage dropped to 7% by using classifier Gamma.",
    "It is important to mention that we defined stable mixtures as the ones where the score of the \"Stable\" classification-a rough approximation of predicted probability-was higher than 50%."
  ]
}